title: The Great Bongo Heist
description: The boys forget to get Chata a gift for Abuela Day and in a panicked move, they pretend that the bongo drums they borrowed from Xochi are for her. Knowing they have to return the drums, Victor & Valentino pretend to be burglars to steal the bongos back.

title: Hurricane Chata
description: When V & V discover that Chata's emotions control the water in the lake, they use it to their advantage and start their own wave pool business.

title: Know It All
description: When Vic accidently unleashes evil bats from a cave, it's up to the boys and Don to protect the town, but Vic's know-it-all attitude keeps getting in the way.

title: It Grows
description: As everyone celebrates Valentino for growing his first facial hair, a jealous Vic resorts to magical methods to grow a mustache and compete for attention.

title: Fistfull of Balloons
description: When Vic gets double-crossed during a water balloon fight, he goes on a revenge mission to find out who was responsible.

title: Suerte
description: When Vic cheats on an enchanted board game, the malevolent characters come to life, and it's up to V & V to figure out how to put them back in the game.

title: Chata's Quinta Quinceañera
description: Vic and Val want to go to a friend's pool party on the same day as their grandma's quinceañera, so they use a magical flute that allows them to teleport and attend both at the same time.

title: A New Don
description: When Vic & Val discover that Don isn't really himself, it's up to them to use his kooky codex of conspiracies to save him.

title: Welcome to the Underworld 2
description: After Vic loses a wrestling match, V&V journey to the underworld to seek advice from their uncle, a famous wrestler named El Toro.

title: Aluxes
description: When Vic finds an ancient relic that summons a gang of mischievous creatures, he uses them to do his bidding, which has disastrous consequences.

title: Guillermo's Gathering
description: When Vic & Val are forced to go to Guillermo's boring birthday party, they devise a scheme to leave early, but end up discovering that the party is way cooler than they thought.

title: Churro Kings
description: When Vic & Val start making good money from selling churros at the taco stand, their lust for stuff makes them do dirty tricks to take out their competition.

title: Balloon Boys
description: Vic & Val go on a hot air balloon trip with Sal and compete to be his favorite, but things go awry when they try to use the magical Nazca Lines to their advantage.

title: The Babysitter
description: Vic & Val want to sneak out to a secret fireworks show but are thwarted when their new babysitter, Xochi, outsmarts them at every turn.

title: Folk Art Foes
description: When Vic accidently unleashes the lord of mischief from an ancient relic, V and V have to work together to trap it back inside.

title: Boss For a Day
description: When Chata lets Vic be the boss of the taco stand for the day Vic decides to fire Val, which has disastrous consequences.

title: Cleaning Day
description: Victor & Valentino gain a newfound respect for cleanliness after Chata's house traps them inside its labyrinth of ancient, magical walls.

title: Ener-G-Shoes
description: When Vic uses trickery to buy a pair of super cool sneakers from Maria Teresa's yard sale, the shoes try to walk him to his demise as punishment.

title: Legend of the Hidden Skate Park
description: While searching for a hidden skate park, V and V happen upon a tribe of wild kids, who live in a society without rules or adults.

title: Lonely Haunts Club
description: Instead of celebrating Valentine's Day, Vic & Val take on a dare to explore a haunted mansion with their rivals, Charlene & Pineapple.

title: Dead Ringer
description: When Vic doesn't pick Val for his soccer team, Val vows to win with his own squad. But when his team doesn't match up, he resorts to supernatural means to win.

title: The Boy Who Cried Lechuza
description: After faking an injury to get out of work, Vic gains sympathy from everyone while unknowingly attracting attention from a dangerous mythical creature.

title: Love at First Bite
description: Val crushes on a girl named Matty, who Vic is suspicious of but Val ignores his warnings. When Val goes to dinner at her house she turns into a Matlazihua and he discovers he's what's for dinner!

title: Welcome to the Underworld 1
description: After Vic loses a wrestling match, V&V journey to the underworld to seek advice from their uncle, a famous wrestler named El Toro.

title: Go With the Flow
description: When Sal stays with Vic & Val, the boys are annoyed by him as their roommate but eventually they learn how cool and magical he is.

title: The Dark Room
description: After getting rejected by a photography club, Val tries to get a picture of the legendary Chupacabra in order to prove himself.

title: The Collector
description: When Vic accidentally loses one of Val's prized coins Val makes a deal with a mysterious antiques collector to replace it, but the deal has terrible consequences.

title: Brotherly Love
description: After breaking Chata's plant, Vic and Val must accomplish the seemingly easy task of replacing it; this proves difficult when their squabbling puts Monte Macabre in jeopardy.

title: Los Cadejos
description: Val holds a grudge against Vic, unwittingly attracting an evil cadejo, a mythological wolf-like beast.

title: Cuddle Monster
description: After being told by Chata that they can't get a pet, Vic & Val adopt a wild lizard, unaware of its magical properties, and decide to keep it secret from Chata.
